  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Sevoflurane is widely used for induction of anaesthesia. Several studies showed EEG
      abnormalities during mask induction with sevoflurane. The aim of our study was to test the
      induction target concentration of sevoflurane on the spikes wave occurrence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
